        <abstract> 
<p>Discusses recent reviews of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> and has made a note on Owen’s [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">2737</hi>].</p> 
            <p>Has become interested in the floral structures of orchids.</p> 
<p>Notes his recent observations on <hi rend="italic">Primula</hi>; believes he has found male and female forms.</p> 
        </abstract>
